ory time", "sentence": [{"id": 1042, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 1, "title": "Look at my summer vacation plan!", "content": "", "duration": 3350, "en_title": "看看我的暑假计划!", "end_timestamp": 13375, "start_timestamp": 10025}, {"id": 1043, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 2, "title": "It''s April now. The summer vacation is still three months away.", "content": "", "duration": 5175, "en_title": "现在是4月。离暑假还有三个月。", "end_timestamp": 20375, "start_timestamp": 15200}, {"id": 1044, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 3, "title": "Early planning is always good.", "content": "", "duration": 3350, "en_title": "提前计划总是好的。", "end_timestamp": 25475, "start_timestamp": 22125}, {"id": 1045, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 4, "title": "In July I''ll visit my grandparents. They live in Xinjiang.", "content": "", "duration": 5325, "en_title": "7月我将去看望我的祖父母。他们住在新疆。", "end_timestamp": 33050, "start_timestamp": 27725}, {"id": 1046, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 5, "title": "What will you do there?", "content": "", "duration": 1950, "en_title": "你会在那里做什么?", "end_timestamp": 36800, "start_timestamp": 34850}, {"id": 1047, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 6, "title": "We''ll go to Grape Valley. The grapes there are very sweet! Grapes are my favourite fruit!", "content": "", "duration": 8750, "en_title": "我们要去葡萄谷。那里的葡萄很甜!葡萄是我最喜欢的水果!", "end_timestamp": 46125, "start_timestamp": 37375}, {"id": 1048, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 7, "title": "In August, I''ll go to Huangshan Mountain. The trees there are very famous. The clouds are beautiful!", "content": "", "duration": 9300, "en_title": "8月，我将去黄山。那里的树很有名。云是美丽的!", "end_timestamp": 56400, "start_timestamp": 47100}, {"id": 1049, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 8, "title": "Sounds great!", "content": "", "duration": 2275, "en_title": "听起来太棒了!", "end_timestamp": 60325, "start_timestamp": 58050}, {"id": 1050, "role": null, "audio": null, "order": 9, "title": "You have a great plan, but what will you do t